1
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:56,400
Leave if you want.

2
00:01:00,680 --> 00:01:02,240
I'll ask you one last time.

3
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:06,220
Are you leaving

4
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,520
or not?

5
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:21,400
Hello?

6
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:22,300
Hey, mechanic.

7
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,400
What's the meaning of leaving

8
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,240
me alone here?

9
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,400
Are you coming back or not?

10
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,000
I'm coming. What's the rush?

11
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,200
Junior.

12
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,039
Thank you for giving me this chance.

13
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:36,600
Su Wan.

14
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:37,960
Who is this person?

15
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,820
I'm really sorry about last time.

16
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:42,759
But I hope you won't misunderstand me.

17
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:44,720
So?

18
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,520
What are you trying to say?

19
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,280
There's a pretty good restaurant ahead.

20
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,320
Let's talk while we eat.

21
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:51,240
Is it the person who called Su Wan?

22
00:01:51,759 --> 00:01:52,690
It's just ahead.

23
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,650
Let's go.

24
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,600
You look really beautiful tonight.

25
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:34,840
Su Wan.

26
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:36,610
To be honest,

27
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,960
I've really fallen for you.

28
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,720
Be with me.

29
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,329
It's impossible for us.

30
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,400
Senior,

31
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:45,079
I only came out to make it clear to you again.

32
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,890
I already have a boyfriend.

33
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,079
So please don't bother me anymore.

34
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,440
I tolerated it when you said it once.

35
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,480
But it's meaningless to say it so many times.

36
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,880
What's so good about him?

37
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,960
If you are with me,

38
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:02,560
I can cherish you every day

39
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,360
and let you live like a princess.

40
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:06,220
Tell me, how am I not as good as him?

41
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,760
Can't you understand me?

42
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,440
I already told you I have a boyfriend.

43
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,280
Stop pestering me.

44
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,720
I actually know you really want to be with me.

45
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,640
Don't play hard to get with me.

46
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,720
I have already told you

47
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,480
that I like you.

48
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:20,610
Just take the way out I'm offering you.

49
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,000
Him?

50
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,960
Yes, it's him.

51
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,680
And I only like him.

52
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,120
You know what?

53
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:55,380
No one has ever rejected me in my life.

54
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,320
You are the first.

55
00:03:58,079 --> 00:04:00,210
I have something to do. I'll get going.

56
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:05,440
Su Wan.

57
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,120
Are you crazy?

58
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,250
You bastard, Gao Chenyang.

59
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,680
Why are you so late? What are you good for?

60
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,959
You let her get bullied right under your nose.

61
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,120
Junior Sister Su Wan,

62
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,560
you might have misunderstood me.

63
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,820
I am not what you think.

64
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,040
You're unlucky to have met me.

65
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,900
I'm a black belt in Taekwondo.

66
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,760
Su Wan.

67
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:30,840
Su Wan,

68
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,280
look at me.

69
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:43,240
You won't be scared if you don't see it.

70
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:49,400
I have really rejected him many times.

71
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,290
If I catch you again,

72
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,970
I'll beat you up every time.

73
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,640
I'm here.

74
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,160
It's okay.

75
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:18,400
What?

76
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,610
I can't believe this happened.

77
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,090
We must call the police.

78
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,240
Who knows what that jerk

79
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,600
will do next time.

80
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:27,800
Forget it.

81
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,500
Otherwise, my mom will nag me for 3 years.

82
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,360
Besides, calling the police

83
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,400
will only solve today's problem.

84
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,159
There are so many jerks in the world.

85
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:36,760
What if you meet the next one?

86
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,800
You should learn taekwondo with me.

87
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,560
No, no, no.

88
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,880
My cousin is such a sweet

89
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:42,720
and cute girl.

90
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,440
How can she learn taekwondo?

91
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,610
What do you mean?

92
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,480
I didn't mean anything else.

93
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:54,720
I just think

94
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:57,960
Taekwondo is too violent.

95
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,080
It's not suitable for a girl.

96
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,040
Ouch.

97
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:06,040
Su Wan, did you see that?

98
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,600
Do this next time you meet a jerk.

99
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,680
Just you wait.

100
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,440
You'll definitely regret this.

101
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:08,600
Look at the time.

102
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,810
Why isn't your sister back yet?

103
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,770
She's coming back later and later.

104
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:17,760
Do you think

105
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,760
she's dating someone?

106
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:25,960
Probably

107
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,260
just stressed from studying lately.

108
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,720
Besides,

109
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,880
she's a little girl going through puberty.

110
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,080
To a bunch of grown men like us,

111
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:36,000
what could she possibly have to say?

112
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,200
Alright, stop worrying.

113
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,060
I'll go find her right now.

114
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,200
Hurry up.

115
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,260
Sit for a while.

116
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,400
Dad, Brother, I'm back.

117
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:46,810
You're back.

118
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,050
Where did you go?

119
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,200
Wait.

120
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,380
Why are your clothes so dirty?

121
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,400
We had a class cleanup today.

122
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:59,000
I'm a little tired. I'll go upstairs to rest.

123
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,840
You should rest early too.

124
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,400
Bai Qing.

125
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:06,100
Nothing happened, right?

126
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:10,160
You're not dating anyone, are you, Bai Qing?

127
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,440
You are going to be a senior soon, right?

128
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,120
Brother.

129
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,120
I promised you I would study hard

130
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,840
and get into the best university.

131
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,170
I will definitely do it.

132
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:20,080
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

133
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,740
Come home earlier from now on.

134
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,360
Then I'll go back to my room to rest.

135
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:26,960
Go ahead.

136
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,160
Don't miss out as you pass by.

137
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,480
Get a membership and receive a free car inspection.

138
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,280
50% off all repairs. Take a look.

139
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:49,680
No, thanks.

140
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,280
Don't miss out!

141
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,760
50% off on all repairs.

142
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:55,720
Free car inspection with membership. Take a look.

143
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,800
Why are you looking at me?

144
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,530
Follow my lead and shout it out.

145
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,360
Just standing here

146
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,840
won't bring in any business.

147
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,080
There are so many people inside.

148
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,280
You might as well go in and help explain.

149
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,680
Standing here posing

150
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,420
won't attract any customers.

151
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,160
Step right up!

152
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,620
Brother, have some water.

153
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:15,850
Did you get hurt?

154
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:18,680
I'm fine.

155
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:21,640
Why don't you go inside and greet the customers first?

156
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,560
I'll go get some medicine.

157
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,490
I'm really fine.

158
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,240
It's okay.

159
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,450
Don't be so reckless next time.

160
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,810
You bumped into her.

161
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:33,090
Don't listen to your brother's nonsense.

162
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,040
Su Wan, let me help you inside.

163
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,800
No need. I can do it myself.

164
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,010
I'll go in first.

165
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,000
Su Wan, I...
